---
title: Easy Turkey Chilli with kidney beans, cheesy topping and fluffy rice
description: Chilli is a classic dish in the wonderful world of Tex-Mex cuisine, which explains the Mexican influences in this recipe. Along with spiced and simmered turkey mince, you'll also find fluffy rice for scooping up your stew and a sprinkling of cheese for added tastiness.
